{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "3eed3aab-b980-4e17-b3fc-3381b3bd6f0c", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/3eed3aab-b980-4e17-b3fc-3381b3bd6f0c@1.pkg/1772597640913/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597641784", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/3eed3aab-b980-4e17-b3fc-3381b3bd6f0c@1.pkg/1772597640913/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597641784"}, "identifier": "3eed3aab-b980-4e17-b3fc-3381b3bd6f0c", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>这道题目考查</span><span>学生</span><span>对</span><span>具体情境的</span><span>的分析</span><span>和价值判断</span><span>能力。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①</span><span>\"蹲下拨流苏\"体现对残障学生的人格尊重</span><span>，对材料内容分析正确；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③</span><span>\"考虑坐轮椅者需求\"展现换位思考</span><span>，对材料内容分析正确；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②④</span><span>属于规则意识和职责范畴，与题干体现的人文关怀不符</span><span>。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>因此，正确答案为</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①③</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">，选</span><span>A</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（原创）</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">2025年6月，某高校毕业典礼上，校长主动蹲下为坐轮椅的学生拨正流苏。这一行为主要体现了（ ）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①人格平等，尊重特殊群体尊严</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②遵守校规，严格执行典礼流程</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③换位思考，考虑他人实际需求</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④履行职责，完成校长分内工作</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（原创）2025年6月，某高校毕业典礼上，校长主动蹲下为坐轮椅的学生拨正流苏。这一行为主要体现了（ ）①人格平等，尊重特殊群体尊严②遵守校规，严格执行典礼流程③换位思考，考虑他人实际需求④履行职责，完成校长分内工作", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/3eed3aab-b980-4e17-b3fc-3381b3bd6f0c@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984622004", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①③</span><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-